These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, zucchini, radish, lemon
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indonesian, russian, french
1. the indonesian is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person eating onion is the french##1
3. the russian is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the french##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | radish | zucchini | onion   |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | brazilian     | russian   | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, dancing, baking, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, handball, basketball, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | baking | traveling | dancing | chess    |
| Sport   | basketball    | handball      | water-polo | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, reading, skydiving, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, superhero, animation, horror
1. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | card-games | chess | skydiving   | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | animation | horror | superhero         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, comedy, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, badminton, rowing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | adventure | zombie  | comedy      |
| Sport         | badminton | swimming   | rowing | skateboarding |

