.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, corn, apricot, papaya
4 different pets are kept: goat, bird, guinea-pig, cat
1. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating onion##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | papaya | apricot | corn | onion |
| Pet    | goat       | cat | guinea-pig | bird     |

