.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, chinese, thai, colombian
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, lizard, snake
1. the chinese is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the thai##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the thai##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai | american | chinese |
| Pet           | rabbit      | lizard | snake | rat    |

