2. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
3. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | metal | house | reggae | trance  |
| Pet           | hamster | bird | pony       | rabbit |

