.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, security-guard, engineer, teacher
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, airplane, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the teacher##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the accountant##1
4. the engineer is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | engineer | accountant      | security-guard | teacher |
| Transport   | motorbike          | bike | airplane     | snowmobile    |

