2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | juice | mirinda  | fanta | almond-milk |
| Transport   | boat | skateboard | airplane          | trike    |

