.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, malaysian, indian, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski, tram, bike
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the russian##1
3. the french is on the left of the indian##1
4. the russian is the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | french | indian | malaysian | russian   |
| Transport     | tram  | taxi    | jet-ski       | bike |

 